CREATE TABLE DimDate (
    Date date,
    Year int,
    Quarter int,
    Month int,
    Day int,
    Weekday varchar(20),
    Weekday_Number int,
    Is_Weekend bit,
    Day_Of_Year int,
    Date_String varchar(10)
)
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = replicate,
    CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
